_sText:
My first crack at a CSS map.  Vietnam like map.

Comes in some diffrent flavors as I figured things out better

Chupong-  was first version.  walls are solid green color and close
to border.  Actually is is very hard to see bots on this.
                                                            good for gungame?

Chupong 2- version has more trees and they are oriented randomly.
           Walls and roof are solid green box.  basic
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Chupong sky-  this version has skybox, but due to my floor mistake,
              the rocks and hills are highest in this one. This version
              has a dark border out in skybox

Chupong sky2- I raised the floor so the hills are lower and
              there are paths between the mounds.  
------------------------------------------------------

Chupong2sky4- this one is the Chupong 2 version with full,
              un walled outer area.  It is full sky through the
              trees.  White camo is weirdly effective.

Chupong2sky5-  this is same map,  but with the dark green border
               out in the skybox edge.  Looks like dark horizon
               in treeline.



I am including the Silverbirch.rar file as it is custom
static prop I used.  I tried to compile map into complete
bsp with pakrat,  but I have no idea what I am doing.
Everything else I think is in a basic install of CSS.

Lighting is basic.  I don't like it shadowy and dark.

I left logs in so you can see my errors and fix them,
map runs,  but I do see some errors.

Please use this on a server,  but I think it will have 
to be compiled with pakrat or some other program.
I could not get it to find or recognize the tree file.

Jigen </;-(>

Credit to they guy who made the silver birches.  Ida used green trees,
but I could not figure out how to get them out of certain maps.

[HG] Custom Gungame!!  Please a version of this on your server!!!
All servers welcome to use,  but i"m on HG gungame most of the time!
